Why am I so scared to post this? üòÖ So, I've been doing a lot of thinking (I always do at the beginning ot the year) and I came to the conclusion that you don't know much about me, so I thought I should get out of my comfort zone and share a bit more of who I am. I love posting content here, but I feel that's only a tiny part of me. That's why I'll do a series of interviews and more personal posts here. I have no idea if you'll like them and the thought of making myself more vulnerable on social media scares me, but I've been wanting to give this a try for a long time, so here I go!
I'd love to know your super honest feedback. Is this something you'll like to see on my account? ;)
That's it! Here goes the first part of my more personal series! ü´∞üèº
